    <h1>Social Selling</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of using social networks — primarily LinkedIn — to find, research, and build relationships with potential buyers before a formal sales conversation. Not cold outreach with a LinkedIn button. <strong>Relationship-first selling that creates warm pipeline.</strong></p>
    <div class="post-meta">
